The '''Kessilian civil wars''' were a series of conflicts fought in the [[Kessel system/Legends|Kessil system]], which contained the planet [[Utapau (Kessil system)|Utapau]]. [[Annikin Starkiller]] fought in these wars, even though he was a teenager.

Some time, probably not long, after the wars, Annikin and his father [[Kane Starkiller]] were living on the [[Fourth Moon of Utapau]] near their derelict [[Kane's ship|spacecraft]].

==Behind the scenes==
In the first draft, Annikin is renamed [[Annikin Starkiller|Justin Valor]]. The planet Utapau is renamed [[Ogana Major|Ogana]]. Both names were rejected or repurposed in later versions.

